reviewText: It's a low budget suspense movie but not bad. There is some tension building wondering how it's going to end. Somewhat predictable ending but still interesting enough to watch once.
Note that this isn't Andrei Tarkovsky's classic 1979 film 'Stalker'. Rather, it's a direct-to-video thriller from 1999. Tarkovsky's 'Stalker' is currently only available on VHS.
